                <div class="tit_nav">
                    <span class="tit_l">您所在位置：</span><a href="/Home/Index">首页</a><b>></b><span>案例信息</span>
                </div>
                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/7373" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-1154</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8798 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">兴衰皆因资金起，莫被侵占是良方 ——海航控股的关联方资金占用风波</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">The rise and fall are all due to capital, and it is a good prescription not to be invaded —— Capital occupation storm of related parties of HNA Holdings</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">李瑞，周博轩，段方琳</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">西安邮电大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">海南航空控股股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">交通运输业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大中型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务资产部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">15 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">关联方；资金占用；海南航空控股股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">related party;  Appropriation of funds;  Hainan Airlines Holding Co. Ltd</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">随着企业经营发展的需要，我国上市公司基本按照《企业内部控制基本规范》制定了相应的的内部控制制度。但是，由于企业股权结构不合理导致控制权相对集中，治理结构不合理，再加上企业的资金控制并没有得到很好的执行，从而企业出现关联方资金占用的情况愈演愈烈。企业资金被占用，不仅影响企业的平稳健康发展损害企业利益，而且严重侵犯了中小股东的权益。因此，防止资金占用问题的发生是保证企业长期健康稳定发展的重要方面。海南航空控股股份有限公司作为我国四大航空公司发展良好。然而，自2019年海航控股首次曝出其存在关联方资金占用问题而导致内部控制审计否定意见的情况后，海航控股就开始走下坡路。随后虽进行了一系列整改，及时追回拆借款，但未能从核心上解决资金占用问题。这使得海航控股在2021年再次曝出影响更为严重的资金占用问题，最终导致海航控股走上破产重整的道路。本案例以海航控股为例，通过其关联方资金占用事件，反映出海航控股在股权结构、治理结构、资金控制上的不合理之处。同时，也为其他企业防治此类问题提供建议。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Along with the needs of the development of business, our listed companies have formulated the corresponding internal control system in accordance with the &quot;basic standard of enterprise internal control&quot;.However, due to the unreasonable ownership structure of the enterprise, the control right is relatively concentrated, the governance structure is not reasonable, and the capital control of the enterprise has not been well implemented, so the situation of related party capital occupation of the enterprise is becoming more and more serious.The occupation of enterprise funds not only affects the steady and healthy development of enterprises and damages the interests of enterprises, but also seriously infringes the rights and interests of minority shareholders.Therefore, preventing the problem of capital occupation is an important aspect to ensure the long-term healthy and stable development of enterprises.Hainan Airlines Holding Co., Ltd. is one of the four major airlines in China.However, HNA has been on a downward spiral since 2019, when it first reported that it was holding funds from related parties that led to a negative internal control audit.Although a series of corrections were made to recover the loan in time, it failed to solve the problem of capital occupation from the core.This led to the exposure of more serious capital occupancy problems in 2021, which eventually led to the bankruptcy reorganization of HNA Holdings.This case takes HNA Holding as an example, and through the capital occupation incident of its related parties, it reflects the unreasonable place in the shareholding structure, governance structure and capital control of HNA Holding.At the same time, it also provides advice for other enterprises to prevent such problems.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2021</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">类别：管理学，适用课程：《内部控制与风险管理》、《审计学》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">内部控制理论；委托代理理论；隧道理论；利益相关者理论；内部人侵占理论；股权制衡理论</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023-06</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
